name: Halo ATV
address: Bedugul, Candikuning, Kec. Baturiti, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82191, Indonesia
review 1: This new ATV spot in Bedugul might be a bit off the beaten path, but that's what makes it feel secluded and exclusive. The tracks are genuinely fantastic and exciting, and the staff members are friendly. You get a glimpse of the lake from the top, and the prices are affordable. Highly recommend!
review 2: The only ATV adventure that includes with documentation (pictures & video) without paying, usually I have to pay around 400k to get all my documentations. The most fun ATV adventure I ever had in Bali with friendly and helpful guide. Riding ATV with cold weather and fog is a new experience for me and I had fun. I took the package that includes with pick up & drop off. Amazing experience, much much recommended!!
review 3: Everyone must come here, the engine quality is very good, different from other places. And the staff is friendly and very alert to maintain customer safety, the spot is also fun!!Thankyouu Haloatv!!!❤️🙌🏻🙌🏻
